WEBVTT

00:06:58.880 --> 00:07:03.536
in three significant chapters
throughout the course of human history:

00:07:03.560 --> 00:07:05.776
local, institutional

00:07:05.800 --> 00:07:08.200
and what we're now entering, distributed.

00:07:08.680 --> 00:07:11.016
So for a long time,

00:07:11.040 --> 00:07:12.296
until the mid-1800s,

00:07:12.320 --> 00:07:16.256
trust was built
around tight-knit relationships.

00:07:16.280 --> 00:07:18.296
So say I lived in a village

00:07:18.320 --> 00:07:20.896
with the first five rows of this audience,

00:07:20.920 --> 00:07:22.856
and we all knew one another,

00:07:22.880 --> 00:07:25.776
and say I wanted to borrow money.

00:07:25.800 --> 00:07:28.776
The man who had his eyes wide open,
he might lend it to me,

00:07:28.800 --> 00:07:30.896
and if I didn't pay him back,